  "worldId": "sci-fi",
  "title": "月环补给站：找到光核",
  "rewards": {
    "growthPoints": 5
  },
  "scenes": [
    {
      "sceneId": "station",
      "background": "assets/story/pixel-worlds-v1/scenes/sci-fi/sf-02.webp",
      "lines": [
        {
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "月环补给站像一只停在月光里的小船。站长把一枚光核藏进了补给箱。",
          "character": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "这里就是月环补给站。我们先把“找到光核”记在地图上。",
          "character": "hero",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "我听到光核在轻轻嗡鸣，信号就在附近。",
          "character": "pet",
          "position": "right"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "先看清蓝色航线，再做一个安全的小动作。",
          "character": "star_engineer",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "activity",
          "activityType": "collect",
          "prompt": "打开带有蓝色光环的补给箱，取出光核。",
          "character": "pet",
          "position": "right",
          "actions": [
            {
              "label": "打开蓝色箱子",
              "feedback": "光核跳了出来，像一颗小小的太阳。"
            },
            {
              "label": "拍拍黄色箱子",
              "feedback": "黄色箱子发出咔哒声，提醒你再找一找。"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "小小探险家完成了第一步，打开蓝色箱子让周围的线索变得清楚起来。",
          "character": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "看！刚才藏起来的线索露出来了。",
          "character": "hero",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "扫描光点后，隐藏的星尘轨迹露出来了。",
          "character": "pet",
          "position": "right"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "把这条轨迹和星图接起来，下一站就会亮起。",
          "character": "star_engineer",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "记住这束光，它会带我们穿过下一段星际航线。",
          "character": "star_engineer",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "我认识了‘光’。光核也愿意和我们一起旅行。",
          "character": "hero",
          "position": "left"
        }
      ],
      "sceneAssets": {
